Package bio.singa.structure.algorithms.superimposition

Class MaximumCommonSubgraphSuperimposer

  • java.lang.Object
    • bio.singa.structure.algorithms.superimposition.SubstructureSuperimposer
      • bio.singa.structure.algorithms.superimposition.MaximumCommonSubgraphSuperimposer
  • public class MaximumCommonSubgraphSuperimposer
extends SubstructureSuperimposer
    The most flexible SubstructureSuperimposer that uses maximum subgraph isomorphism detection to align two structures. As long as there is a shared maximum common subgraph of at least three atoms a meaningful alignment will be produced.
